## Method wich fixes some problems on diffrent browers
#def shrink($name)
html>body $name {
    display: table;
    width: auto;
}
$name {
    white-space:nowrap; /* to force width */
    width:20px;/* rumor is IE should auto-expand  -- doesn't appear true? */
}
#end def

## Main title on the all pages.
